HEADWORD: sign off
<hw>sign` off"</hw> <pr>(s⟦imac⟧n` ⟦add⟧f")</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos>
<def>To terminate a communication, especially one conducted by radio
waves; to terminate a broadcast over radio or television; <as>as, this
is your reporter in Cairo, <ex>signing off</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

